# LivePuzzle Architecture Boundaries

Use this layering order for all new work:
- UI: `lib/screens`, `lib/widgets`
- State: `lib/providers`
- Domain/service: `lib/services`
- Bridge: `plugins/live_photo_bridge/lib`
- Native implementation: `plugins/live_photo_bridge/ios|android`

Rules:
- UI must not call native `MethodChannel` directly; go through bridge/service.
- Prefer extending an existing layer/module over creating parallel `v2` classes with same responsibility.
- New export or media flow changes must keep Flutter and native contracts aligned.
- Keep cross-layer dependency one-way. Do not import higher-layer code into lower layers.

Critical flow reference:
- Editor export path should stay: UI -> service/model -> `LivePhotoBridge` -> native compositor/plugin.
